result.name: Pak Loh Chiu Chow Restaurant

reviews.text:
Yummy soup - pig lungs with almond with teach almond taste. Fresh pomfret fillets - 
Fried pomfret with bitter gourd. 

An old Teo Chiu Restaurnat, a nice place to dine in with family. Still maintained with their quality of food. Reasonable price. Nice service too.

Nice food and service
4
Best Chiu Chow restaurant in town. Friendly and reasonably priced. Try the sliced goose, crab and prawn cakes, dao miu and Chiu Chow noodles
High side of average range. There is private room with two table where is useful for more than 13 till 24.
Authentic Chiuchow restaurant serving quality food, what you pay is what you get
